channel.title: Errror error error
channel.description:
[21:26:16] [Server] Starting loading Cache... java.lang.NullPointerException at dragonkk.rs2rsps.rscache.CacheManager.load(CacheManager.java:18) at dragonkk.rs2rsps.rscache.Cache.<init>(Cache.java:16) at dragonkk.rs2rsps.Server.<init>(Server.java:35) at dragonkk.rs2rsps.Server.main(Server.java:57) Press any key to continue . . .
Seriously? What is wrong with this error. It's something to do with the cache when I've moved it to C:\...

item.title: Errror error error
item.dc:creator: @gergy008 gergy008
item.description:
@gergy008 wrote:

I had the EXACT same error today. Noone helped me but I figured it out on my own like always anyway. The reason for this is the cache directory is wrong in one of the files. Try cache.java at line 16 or server.java at line 35, Make sure it’s named correctly.
